 {'action': 'created', 'author': 'gerrywastaken', 'comment_id': 639442176.0, 'datetime': '2020-06-05 12:07:58+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_10', 'text': "@username_5 @username_9  I'm a bit confused by the summary of this issue. I read thought this:
